    "statement": "aku-035-surveillance-protocols is a fundamental concept in Health-Sciences Medicine Surgery Vascular Pathology Mesenteric-Ischemia that provides essential knowledge for understanding related topics and clinical/practical applications.",
    "explanation": {
      "intuition": "Understanding aku-035-surveillance-protocols helps build foundational knowledge. The concept connects to broader principles in the field.",
